-origin=\"off\">Options for creating a compiler.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/CompilerOptions#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"type-alias-overview\">\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n    type <a href=\"api/core/CompilerOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">CompilerOptions</a> = {\n    useJit?: boolean;\n    defaultEncapsulation?: <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation</a>;\n    providers?: <a href=\"api/core/StaticProvider\" class=\"code-anchor\">StaticProvider</a>[];\n    missingTranslation?: <a href=\"api/core/MissingTranslationStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">MissingTranslationStrategy</a>;\n    preserveWhitespaces?: boolean;\n};\n    </code-example>\n  </section>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/CompilerOptions#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">用於建立編譯器的選項</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Note: the <code>useJit</code> and <code>missingTranslation</code> config options are not used in Ivy, passing them has\nno effect. Those config options are deprecated since v13.</p>\n\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/COMPILER_OPTIONS\n - api/core/CompilerFactory\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/PlatformRef\n - api/platform-browser-dynamic/JitCompilerFactory\n - api/upgrade/UpgradeAdapter\n - guide/deprecations\n - guide/update-to-version-14\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/CompilerOptions#compileroptions\n - api/core/CompilerOptions#description\n - api/core/MissingTranslationStrategy\n - api/core/StaticProvider\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/linker/compiler.ts?message=docs(core)%3A